{"tid":403652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"庫爾德月底獨立公投,伊拉克政府警告不排除武裝介入","createTime":"2017-09-17T11:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T11:47:11.000Z","uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23b2ce625670f17577cd91e4b466aaa5a54f9d5d","tid":403652,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1658867/%E4%BC%8A%E6%8B%89%E5%85%8B%E5%BA%AB%E7%88%BE%E5%BE%B7%E6%97%8F%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E5%8D%80%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%AC%E6%8A%95+%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%95%E6%86%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1658867%2F%25E4%25BC%258A%25E6%258B%2589%25E5%2585%258B%25E5%25BA%25AB%25E7%2588%25BE%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E6%2597%258F%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%25BA%2595%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E6%258A%2595%2B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E9%2581%2595%25E6%2586%25B2&d=GZt96%2FKv4wIU%2FOEQMyNF7TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a404103e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1658867/%E4%BC%8A%E6%8B%89%E5%85%8B%E5%BA%AB%E7%88%BE%E5%BE%B7%E6%97%8F%E8%87%AA%E6%B2%BB%E5%8D%80%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E5%85%AC%E6%8A%95+%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%A8%B1%E9%81%95%E6%86%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n庫爾德族自治區議會通過月底舉行獨立公投。伊拉克政府強調獨立公投違反憲法，總理阿巴迪警告，不排除軍事介入。鄰國土耳其、伊朗等亦反對舉行公投，土耳其表示，會採取必要行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打完ISIS, 又輪到庫爾德人vs伊拉克"},{"pid":"c3786944bc6b61308e74639b7c7712e790211941","tid":403652,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:12:31.000Z","msg":"庫族公投爭獨立　美反對<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170917/20155284\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170917%2F20155284&d=GZt96%2FKv4wIU%2FOEQMyNF7TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=98bc25c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170917%2F20155284&h=39d8117e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170917/20155284</a><br />\n<br />\n美國之前又話支持, 家陣又縮沙"},{"pid":"ae2dd5aeec25dcc3cecf3fc384e97012f55fe4f4","tid":403652,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c917706c851ad164794c48803f3ac08e78abd129","tid":403652,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T11:58:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc908d82df6846e5b34bc27335469c0783d30f0","tid":403652,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:33:09.000Z","msg":"無人關心?<br />\n庫爾德人同香港人一樣, 都是要獨立<br />\n<br />\n但庫爾德人處境更危險<br />\n<br />\n要面對土耳其, 伊拉克, 敘利亞, 伊朗 四個中東國家<br />\n仲有美國又唔想支持佢地, 以免得罪太多國家<br />\n<br />\n但以色列 就反而支持佢地<br />\n因為以色列想減弱 中東各國既實力<br />\n同埋庫爾德人 雖然都係信伊斯蘭教, 但佢地思想比較親西方, 唔會受伊斯蘭教 既教條約束, 即係唔會有.....反西方/反以色列......女人要包頭巾, 之類既on9野"},{"pid":"6e35eee9334ce32804406facb0b9e8a191fe5717","tid":403652,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"連登仔連英國恐襲都唔理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2f2802207aba1abbf8f0c74d8b812db29b7778","tid":403652,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔連英國恐襲都唔理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n英國恐襲 關香港咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但庫爾德人獨立, 明顯同香港好相關<br />\n香港可以向 庫爾德人借鏡"},{"pid":"419986863dbef4b74c484188f8c0843badc4405b","tid":403652,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:47:11.000Z","msg":"庫爾德人獨立,其實真係有齊天時, 地利, 人和<br />\n<br />\n天時<br />\n2003年, 美國出兵伊拉克, 庫爾德人協助美軍......戰後獲得自治<br />\n2014年, ISIS掘起, 攻打庫爾德地區..........庫爾德人勇武抵抗, 增加國際威望<br />\n<br />\n地利<br />\n庫爾德地區多山, 易守難攻<br />\n<br />\n人和<br />\n庫爾德人十分勇武, 由二戰後, 就一直勇武爭取獨立, 與伊拉克政府打游擊戰<br />\n<br />\n如果咁都唔獨立, 真係無天理"}]}